{"tid":1344681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警總餐廳辭職經理","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:50.000Z","uid":125079,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64386cbd1d0a148928df61e73372305f05775461","tid":1344681,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:08:10.000Z","msg":"原任經理的徐逸昇6.12一直留在警總的餐廳，那裏全天候播着無綫新聞，「正常係唔可以轉台」。肉體收取警員的飯錢，靈魂卻穿透餐廳玻璃落在血腥夏慤道：「一個媽咪企咗喺防暴警察面前，攤開隻手，叫佢哋唔好射啲細路，人哋同你講緊愛嘅時候，警察就兜頭射落去，我嗰吓嬲到呢&hellip;&hellip;另一個女仔俾一班警察追捕，佢跌咗落地，成班警察瘋狂咁毆打佢。<span style=\"color: red;\">你身為警察，身穿制服，你打女人，仲要一大班人打女人，黑社會都唔會做啦</span>，我真係好嬲，我接受唔到佢哋呢啲行為。嗰日我嬲到瞓唔着覺。」<br />\n<br />\n徐生你錯啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">黑社會唔撚止會打女人, 仲會打撚埋大肚婆</span><br />\n<br />\n仆街黑警包庇黑社會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝你地仆街死</span>"},{"pid":"679b8b4d67f3799e77f71d57fd6a40e78da66c29","tid":1344681,"uid":175316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c09dc1a8f54892890a76bd42f8093cd6f79368","tid":1344681,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 寫咗個白宮聯署<br />\nrequest國際人道救援/援助<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c5a6c53b218c3511933f172c31bfe305f50ff686","tid":1344681,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"黑社會黎架徐生"},{"pid":"00bad513cd38bc1f28e07adaa95c57bc2c4eed19","tid":1344681,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20